intellij:
ctrl space	-> suggestions
ctrl shift space -> smart suggestion
option enter -> for quick fixes
double shift -> search everywhere
cmd shift U -> toggle case
cmd shift A  or double shift -> action (like about or show line numbers)

cmd O(alphabet) -> *imp* to search classes (select 'all places' in drop down to search in libs as well)

opt up -> select line or block etc
cmd / -> comment
cmd d -> duplicate line
cmd del -> delete line
opt shift up/down -> move line
cmd shift up/down -> move entire method
cmd - -> collapse
cmd = -> expand
cmd shift - -> collapse all
cmd opt T -> *imp* surround code with try catch etc
ctrl g, ctrl cmd g -> to select all occurrences of work/symbol
(expr). -> dot after expression gives post complete options

cmd shift enter -> *imp* to complete statement
ctrl space then tab -> to replace the current value with suggested value

shift fn F6 -> *imp* to rename

cmd opt v -> to extract to a local variable

ctrl + t -> *imp* refactoring menu

right click (local history) *imp*

cmd opt l  -> format code, just for selected block, select block and use the short cut

cmd p -> parameter info of the method

cmd f1 -> warning description
opt shift f7 / just cmd f-> *imp* highlight all symbols

cmd shift f  and cmd shift r -> *imp* find in file, replace in file

cnd f12 -> file structure, see all methods, you can also search jst start typing the name of method etc

cmd b / cmd opt b (interfaces) / opt f7(detailed)-> *imp* show all calling places of method

shift esc -> closes view

cmd 3 -> opens view


cmd e -> *imp* recently opened files
cmd shift e -> with code fragment

cmd f -> to find and highlight symbol/word

ctrl shift r -> run main class

debugging:
expressions to debug
cmd opt f8 show quick evaluation
